<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
	<title>Project Processing, Appraisal & Management System (PPS)</title>
	<style>
		body {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			background-color: #f4f4f4;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}
		.container {
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 20px auto;
			background-color: #ffffff;
			border: 1px solid #dddddd;
			box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			border-radius: 8px;
			overflow: hidden;
		}
		.header {
			text-align: center;
			padding: 20px;
			background-color: #EFF5F5;
			color: #333333;
		}
		.header img {
			max-width: 120px;
			height: auto;
		}
		.header h2 {
			margin: 10px 0 0 0;
			font-size: 24px;
			color: #0056b3;
		}
		.content {
			text-align: left;
			padding: 20px;
			color: #333333;
		}
		.content p {
			line-height: 1.6;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}
		.button-container {
			text-align: center;
			margin: 20px 0;
		}
		.button-container a {
			background-color: #0056b3;
			color: #ffffff;
			border: none;
			padding: 10px 20px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			cursor: pointer;
			font-size: 16px;
			text-decoration: none;
		}
		.button-container button:hover {
			background-color: #004494;
			cursor: pointer;
		}
		.footer {
			text-align: center;
			padding: 20px;
			background-color: #EFF5F5;
			color: #666666;
			font-weight: bold;
		}
		.footer span {
			display: block;
		}
		@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
			.container {
				width: 100%;
				margin: 0;
				border-radius: 0;
			}
			.content, .header, .footer {
				padding: 15px;
			}
			.button-container button {
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
	<div class="header">
		<img src="https://gedkp.gov.bd/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/155-1559388_bangladesh-government-logo-png-bangladesh-govt-logo-png-400x420.jpg" alt="Logo">
		<h2>Project Processing, Appraisal & Management System (PPS)</h2>
	</div>
	<div class="content">
		<p>Dear Sir,</p>
		<p>We are pleased to inform you that a new development project has been assigned to you through PPS Software. Please find the project details below:</p>
		<div class="button-container">
			<a href="https://sso.plandiv.gov.bd/sign-in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Project Detail View</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="footer">
		<span>Best regards,</span>
		<span>PPS Software Team</span>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
